{"tid":61014,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[高質]裕滿人家係我去過最正既酒樓","createTime":"2016-12-31T01:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T16:08:47.000Z","uid":7775,"like":240,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aea8f6ba33f79e5a9a1f7a57b6718f8f661db49b","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T01:15:23.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母啦，d野難食不在話下<br />\n有無諗過咁大個集團，竟然可以利用法律榨取13年員工既年假同血汗錢<br />\n<br />\n經濟<br />\n<a href=\"http://topick.hket.com/article/1610380/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1610380%2F&d=lcsPd6LPR%2BRuyxh63d%2BwSQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=6b20fc54\" target=\"_blank\">http://topick.hket.com/article/1610380/</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56109729&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56109729%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161230&d=lcsPd6LPR%2BRuyxh63d%2BwSQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=117e68a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56109729%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161230&h=5b8322d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56109729&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161230</a><br />\n<br />\n(酒樓的持有人與其餘兩名股東，3人各自成立公司，每18個月就以甲公司名義與僱員簽約，到第19個月則以現金支票出糧，以「過冷河」，並再以乙公司名義與僱員簽署新合約，如此類推)<br />\n<br />\n而家話炒就炒，補一個禮拜代通知金就算，上到庭淨係畀600和解當豪乞兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n法律係制裁唔到佢<br />\n但作為連登巴絲<br />\n好希望大家略盡棉力，團結抵制依種奸商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後會有幾波狙擊行動"},{"pid":"f09f2adf900afba2f36414bd464f269e759f0558","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T01:20:17.000Z","msg":"明白會有巴絲覺得<br />\n<br />\n點解唔搵份好工？<br />\n<br />\n有學歷讀到書邊個唔想？<br />\n<br />\n但係咪代表社會最底層就注定畀人欺壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840341b3d999a6203d0d44def99e078b206e0eae","tid":61014,"uid":44807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T01:40:34.000Z","msg":"支持留明"},{"pid":"8d17e0111dd7c08416df491a2bba6cd615f7d2f8","tid":61014,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T01:44:11.000Z","msg":"咁仲有人做？<br />\nBTW 咁仆街唔推唔得"},{"pid":"e8b55033c3ce03d739cc992ced68dafe4914fd76","tid":61014,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T01:45:25.000Z","msg":"仆街公司"},{"pid":"e34c3c8769e186f393c85bc2a82ca63f8b8ebd5e","tid":61014,"uid":47210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T01:51:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982dc4a9da5f7c12598dc3bc9f60234771ae0360","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T01:54:09.000Z","msg":"當大家滿足口腹之慾既同時<br />\n<br />\n都請關注一下為你地服務既人既權利<br />\n<br />\n而家只係好基本勞工權益"},{"pid":"fa826600b2a25802f1db18a3414ab826a43f6d34","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T01:54:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁仲有人做？<br />\nBTW 咁仆街唔推唔得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無計，飲食業仆街公司多"},{"pid":"6e6e8ce0e232c7b680d6150bf232e7a178005d52","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:00:03.000Z","msg":"第一炮，請巴絲登入open rice<br />\n幫手畀個<span style=\"color: red;\">差評</span><br />\n<br />\n寫既內容切記唔好提及佢既道德問題<br />\n<br />\n多講佢d餸幾咁難食、服務態度差之類<br />\n<br />\n菜式參考，自由作文：<br />\n■ 文昌雞<br />\n■ 蛋白蒸龍躉扒<br />\n■ 京式玉帶賽螃蟹<br />\n■ 清蒸東星斑<br />\n■ 雞油花雕蒸紅蟹<br />\n■ 亂棍炒翡翠<br />\n■ 如意吉祥露筍<br />\n■ 朱紅武御膳豆腐<br />\n■ 鄉下筒仔飯<br />\n<br />\n元朗<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS083C000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS083C000&d=lcsPd6LPR%2BRuyxh63d%2BwSQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=0870060b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS083C000</a><br />\n<br />\n慈雲山<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0hKi000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0hKi000&d=lcsPd6LPR%2BRuyxh63d%2BwSQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=73818a55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0hKi000</a><br />\n<br />\n東涌<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0Pz60W0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0Pz60W0&d=lcsPd6LPR%2BRuyxh63d%2BwSQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=06a6a8ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0Pz60W0</a><br />\n<br />\n火炭<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0y54000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0y54000&d=lcsPd6LPR%2BRuyxh63d%2BwSQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=ac6e8973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0y54000</a><br />\n<br />\n葵涌<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS08ZC000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS08ZC000&d=lcsPd6LPR%2BRuyxh63d%2BwSQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=81cf7a3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS08ZC000</a>"},{"pid":"6b78f328f95ff6928e634a8214b6d93997f1e434","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:14:29.000Z","msg":"第二炮，打電話去訂位<br />\n<br />\n東涌逸東邨逸東商場217號舖<br />\n電話：2325 8555 傳真：2325 8321<br />\n<br />\n新界元朗鳳翔路2至6號交通廣場1樓<br />\n電話：2475 1333 傳真：2479 1333<br />\n<br />\n新界火炭駿景廣場G22-G30舖<br />\n電話：2325 8381 傳真：2325 8681<br />\n<br />\n九龍黃大仙毓華街23號慈雲山中心4樓410舖<br />\n電話:2325 6862 傳真：2325 6863<br />\n<br />\n新界葵涌石蔭路64號地下及44-66號1樓<br />\n電話：2387 8666 傳真：2387 8333"},{"pid":"5d80f27e99d8aed319bf27318d7cd08ff4bc461c","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:16:44.000Z","msg":"另徵求懶人包設計<br />\n<br />\n一頁概括即可<br />\n<br />\n方便fb同ig叫人抵制<br />\n<br />\n依兩日無機會電腦，有無人幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f20729ae5170a735a3d12f87e4a2c190ffc6805","tid":61014,"uid":60092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:18:21.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"f368fbf172ef07414a63e3c5434ff54882fcb3a1","tid":61014,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:21:04.000Z","msg":"可恥"},{"pid":"d9b89c4faa4340afbc2821adcd189eab5d37ee24","tid":61014,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfc9a00ce2b083a4d9f358d3e066a050e316cbd","tid":61014,"uid":42977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:21:53.000Z","msg":"執左，改名開過"},{"pid":"834b27f4de1acbe2465697f9be7d1b7a4010012e","tid":61014,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09430cbe7d952482d156c75c219bbff42f2c8373","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:22:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可恥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n的確<br />\n<br />\n走法律la去逃避責任<br />\n<br />\n飲食業大亨莫迪潘發揮到極致<br />\n<br />\n依個亦不遑多讓"},{"pid":"9f542ec2a2aad7f5cc9687806954a4f2c7c98a78","tid":61014,"uid":54060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:23:51.000Z","msg":"推爆佢老母"},{"pid":"a7acf473d37b2fd5937c5916ce80f1081499ac51","tid":61014,"uid":41714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:26:40.000Z","msg":"依家寫臭佢， 之後佢地一樣可以改名， 開過， 無限loop.  仲有咩方法"},{"pid":"b4187f102a5807570edafce9f1036c649e655e9e","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:29:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家寫臭佢， 之後佢地一樣可以改名， 開過， 無限loop.  仲有咩方法</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n裕滿人家個品牌都好多年，唔會改<br />\n<br />\n佢地只係不停咁以不同公司持有依個品牌<br />\n<br />\n而家短期策略係先整爛佢個品牌<br />\n<br />\n會適時推出攻勢，係持久戰<br />\n<br />\n但需要大家團結"},{"pid":"1b888dbdae1407117afbf77fa16c3051e9dac84c","tid":61014,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:31:56.000Z","msg":"裕滿人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d9cfac8cc52e6253e1cc19d0c52780b2686ede","tid":61014,"uid":19093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:37:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>裕滿人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n裕滿我渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb40add26d6ead3c04db17ccaf5f6d9d06c1f9ec","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:37:56.000Z","msg":"如果今次都可以過骨<br />\n<br />\n港豬就真係無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deef147cf103519fcfc618d174860414d4cdd8ae","tid":61014,"uid":66860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:41:56.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"a9201d5a792adfb354e8f7534b2e59fa8d2e724d","tid":61014,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:42:06.000Z","msg":"啲嘢食幾好 睇嚟要多啲訂位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc08999f0f1e2e6c1755165fe77645b76d129b1","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:44:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲嘢食幾好 睇嚟要多啲訂位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係囉，我想食文昌雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caecb2ff53697aa0bae3b2baf474859a0deaf192","tid":61014,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:48:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果今次都可以過骨<br />\n<br />\n港豬就真係無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實港豬一直都冇得救<br />\n<br />\n佢地反而會企係老細角度諗，我真係唔明點解<br />\n<br />\n你睇下依家間酒樓仲有人開緊工就知咩事啦，港奴冇得救架喇"},{"pid":"5db54f4f76922dcce17d9b742649c1b7e18af5c9","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:48:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/TaipoTaipo/permalink/10158098322665245/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2FTaipoTaipo%2Fpermalink%2F10158098322665245%2F&d=lcsPd6LPR%2BRuyxh63d%2BwSQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=9677fafa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/TaipoTaipo/permalink/10158098322665245/</a><br />\n<br />\n幫手分享下<br />\n<br />\n等更多人討論、關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfb6ed1c05ac0c6fca743a27eb1884416285119","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:49:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果今次都可以過骨<br />\n<br />\n港豬就真係無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實港豬一直都冇得救<br />\n<br />\n佢地反而會企係老細角度諗，我真係唔明點解<br />\n<br />\n你睇下依家間酒樓仲有人開緊工就知咩事啦，港奴冇得救架喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係網典admin 饕餮嗎？"},{"pid":"79d85b3a3880ea2d36b82be26ff60b87ab114389","tid":61014,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲嘢食幾好 睇嚟要多啲訂位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係囉，我想食文昌雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有朋友返左香港，想約佢詳談<br />\n可以去酒樓朝早8點傾到下午4點<br />\n野食唔緊要，有杯茶飲已經夠"},{"pid":"5e44045ba3e41eb4f5f53a8fe80ac7b8c07c46db","tid":61014,"uid":24536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:59:11.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e4cf173fdfb2cc10a0e901492453a9ba2a570c","tid":61014,"uid":64227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:01:53.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"31409a67c7319800f0d2aedfe304700266f3b04f","tid":61014,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:23:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"974b739e3f7036a0312c50c6326910a906c2d511","tid":61014,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247a243941a83c93f0b1ee7fb933059ad9c5d44f","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:28:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啲嘢食幾好 睇嚟要多啲訂位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係囉，我想食文昌雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有朋友返左香港，想約佢詳談<br />\n可以去酒樓朝早8點傾到下午4點<br />\n野食唔緊要，有杯茶飲已經夠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫個牛肉球就好"},{"pid":"c9d6e1e1d2f6203f1204d8812d2761b713edf7cd","tid":61014,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:38:16.000Z","msg":"推撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=