wngas.com%2FChi%2FCust%2FBusiness%2FCommerceIndustry%2Fimages%2FApple-v10_FINAL.jpg&h=0aa7e447&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffbdc15916cd009e7ac95c78b6a30d41836b4f37","tid":61014,"uid":49210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:09:41.000Z","msg":"有點樣嘅員工就有點樣嘅老闆， 間酒樓而家嘅工作條件都冇改好吖，一樣有咁多員工喺度，佢哋冇辭工呀。 陣間你諗住好心幫佢， 跟住比佢地話你打爛佢飯碗猶如殺佢哋父母乜乜乜， 我覺得不如等佢哋嘅員工有實際嘅行動先至再行動囉"},{"pid":"1253dcb5bd151cb91ca573970822a0c2dd864831","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:17:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有點樣嘅員工就有點樣嘅老闆， 間酒樓而家嘅工作條件都冇改好吖，一樣有咁多員工喺度，佢哋冇辭工呀。 陣間你諗住好心幫佢， 跟住比佢地話你打爛佢飯碗猶如殺佢哋父母乜乜乜， 我覺得不如等佢哋嘅員工有實際嘅行動先至再行動囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打既意見，亦明白你既顧慮<br />\n<br />\n小弟自知力量無可能打得爛人地飯碗<br />\n<br />\n只期望有限度地影響奸商收入<br />\n<br />\n同喚起關注<br />\n<br />\n溫水煮蛙，留喺依間垃圾公司係咪真係好？"},{"pid":"e2351a4b5e4c0100d218f43cbc486c0838324623","tid":61014,"uid":59922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3eee6f6fef3c5be418191079d6344275879511","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:34:17.000Z","msg":"狙擊行動，越推會越猛"},{"pid":"260f122d7544a2e15239846930baa4785fb7af1d","tid":61014,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:20:48.000Z","msg":"正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97655c5e0bca9b487f7930c29eb2cd9121c1f1d3","tid":61014,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8e5ca749411326762534a0995d7a9f1792beac","tid":61014,"uid":7656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:24:29.000Z","msg":"有咩幫到手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2