ail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F01%2F225703_296f407f9fcc16a73d73476f000477e4.jpg&h=1c4a85d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下一回應有fax詳細教學"},{"pid":"414d3c93a9e591fcd2ee5a6cf6d38573789ac9a7","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T14:59:12.000Z","msg":"東涌逸東邨逸東商場217號舖<br />\n電話：2325 8555 傳真：2325 8321<br />\n<br />\n新界元朗鳳翔路2至6號交通廣場1樓<br />\n電話：2475 1333 傳真：2479 1333<br />\n<br />\n新界火炭駿景廣場G22-G30舖<br />\n電話：2325 8381 傳真：2325 8681<br />\n<br />\n九龍黃大仙毓華街23號慈雲山中心4樓410舖<br />\n電話:2325 6862 傳真：2325 6863<br />\n<br />\n新界葵涌石蔭路64號地下及44-66號1樓<br />\n電話：2387 8666 傳真：2387 8333"},{"pid":"bd335b1fd55e3d0a9255e61bf79c93ac2960234a","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T15:00:33.000Z","msg":"網上Fax 教學<br />\n<br />\n1. 名同姓果d可以隨便作<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/10/16/220740_031df7874fe93791f25166df4e5da332.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F10%2F16%2F220740_031df7874fe93791f25166df4e5da332.jpg&h=5ebf1278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 即刻有email叫你撳link activate<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/10/16/220938_2821cd26222b2f5b6b6a983b4087e888.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F10%2F16%2F220938_2821cd26222b2f5b6b6a983b4087e888.jpg&h=b98ab63f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 登入，然後按compose<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/10/16/221613_84b491c98ed33e0137ffba0b4760bf62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F10%2F16%2F221613_84b491c98ed33e0137ffba0b4760bf62.jpg&h=56dfec1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 上傳個檔案，撳upload<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/10/16/221726_e27faf4bcae4b2f75f6a720fdfb73635.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F10%2F16%2F221726_e27faf4bcae4b2f75f6a720fdfb73635.jpg&h=d7d4488f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 上面撳...揀返頭先個file<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/10/16/221821_752765b0105710b27ffeb0715dc91eae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F10%2F16%2F221821_752765b0105710b27ffeb0715dc91eae.jpg&h=a08e934c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. Cover Page選none，然後右下角Preview<br />\n<br />\n7. FAX<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/10/16/222041_0970901de601d7cab07f40da0b737421.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F10%2F16%2F222041_0970901de601d7cab07f40da0b737421.jpg&h=904dfb3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfd9ed2c9c2c8458df298fc48c2b54cebc026c0d","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T15:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84773c685c92b7f5bc11387cd1972e7ba1d361b5","tid":61014,"uid":39195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T16:28:02.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"2c1ba27634851bb0b6099d759d6f8981001fec08","tid":61014,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T16:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>pish</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c908c7c469a07e18aecb0e54bd3265edc62661d3","tid":61014,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T16:36:28.000Z","msg":"等睇裕滿出一蚊雞忘記件事"},{"pid":"5a8fb7adeb16b1fe6e1a93ae59662d96e940f1d7","tid":61014,"uid":71273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":